# LBM Postprocessing

## Setup

```bash
cd postprocess
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
pip install -e .
```

## Usage

From inside postprocess/:

plot-tke <RUN_ID>

Example:
plot-tke 20260223_170117

The figure will be saved to:
postprocess/outcomes/<RUN_ID>/tke.png
